[SIZE=5][B]ItemMagnet[/B] — Claim-Aware Tiered Item Magnets with Redstone Fuel[/SIZE]

[CENTER][I]Paper 26.1+ · Java 25 · Lands & WorldGuard optional[/I][/CENTER]

[HR]

[B]Compatibility[/B]
[LIST]
[*]Paper 26.1.x (tested on 26.1.2 build 69)
[*]Java 25 required
[*]Optional: Lands, WorldGuard, CMI
[/LIST]

[B]Support[/B]: [URL='https://github.com/RMHavelaar101/item-magent/issues']GitHub Issues[/URL]

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]About[/B][/SIZE]

ItemMagnet adds craftable tiered magnet tools that pull nearby dropped items toward the player with [B]visible, line-of-sight physics[/B] — items slide around corners and stop at walls instead of teleporting through blocks.

Fuel your resonator with [B]redstone dust[/B] (shift+right-click with off-hand) or let it [B]auto-absorb[/B] redstone from the ground. [B]Redstone blocks[/B] provide a power surge — extra charge and temporary radius boost.

Built for survival servers that need [B]Lands[/B] and [B]WorldGuard[/B] respect out of the box, with fully configurable tiers, recipes, unlock gates, and messages.

[SIZE=4][B]Features[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Three tiers (configurable materials, names, radius, drain)
[*]Line-of-sight pull physics with particles
[*]Redstone fuel + power surge system
[*]Lands: wilderness / owner / member / flag modes
[*]WorldGuard: region whitelist/blacklist + item-pickup flag
[*]Unlock gates: permission, advancement, CMI stat/rank, command
[*]Anti-AFK movement check (optional)
[*]Underground vs surface radius modifiers
[/LIST]

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Commands[/B][/SIZE]

[TABLE]
[TR][TH]Command[/TH][TH]Permission[/TH][TH]Description[/TH][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet reload[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.reload[/TD][TD]Reload config[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet version[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.admin[/TD][TD]Version and hook status[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet give <player> <tier> [charge][/TD][TD]itemmagnet.give[/TD][TD]Give a magnet[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet unlock <player> <tier>[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.unlock[/TD][TD]Unlock recipe[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet debug[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.debug[/TD][TD]Debug held magnet[/TD][/TR]
[/TABLE]

[SIZE=4][B]Permissions[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST]
[*][B]itemmagnet.use[/B] (default: true) — use magnets
[*][B]itemmagnet.wilderness[/B] (default: op) — use in Lands wilderness
[*][B]itemmagnet.bypass.lands[/B] — skip Lands checks
[*][B]itemmagnet.bypass.regions[/B] — skip WG region lists
[*][B]itemmagnet.admin[/B] (default: op) — admin commands
[/LIST]

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Configuration[/B][/SIZE]

On first run, edit [CODE]plugins/ItemMagnet/config.yml[/CODE].

Key sections:
[LIST]
[*][B]tiers[/B] — materials, names, radius, recipes, unlocks
[*][B]fuel[/B] — redstone dust vs block charge values
[*][B]integrations.lands[/B] — claim protection
[*][B]integrations.worldguard[/B] — region rules
[*][B]anti-afk[/B] — movement requirement
[*][B]height[/B] — underground radius modifier
[/LIST]

Full reference: [URL='https://github.com/RMHavelaar101/item-magent/blob/main/docs/configuration.md']Configuration docs[/URL]

[HR]

[I]Report bugs on GitHub. Include Paper version, config snippet, and steps to reproduce.[/I]
